Name: TIME SLOT RECURRENCE RATE
Explanation: THE PART OF A TIME SLOT ASSIGNMENT THAT ESTABLISHES THE NUMBER OF ASSIGNED TIME SLOTS SPACED UNIFORMLY OVER EACH EPOCH. IT IS THE POWER OF 2 RANGING FROM 0 TO 15 THAT PROVIDES THE CAPABILITY TO ASSIGN FROM 1 TO 32,768 TIME SLOTS PER EPOCH.

Name: P-MESSAGE TIME SLOT RECURRENCE RATE
Explanation: THE POWER OF 2 THAT ESTABLISHES THE NUMBER OF P-MESSAGE TIME SLOTS.
